    { "version": "2.5.6", "date": "2026-07-01", "summary": "HOTFIX — /update renamed to /pull-scaffold with response fingerprinting and network-call gate. Agents were short-circuiting the multi-step /update command. Fix: (1) renamed primary command to /pull-scaffold; (2) hard-coded network gate at step 1 requiring javascript tool fetch; (3) fingerprint requirement — reply must include manifest.updated_at verbatim. /update and /sync kept as aliases. Install doc seed SQL uses DO UPDATE so re-runs patch existing installs." },
